<p>With the entity API maturing in Drupal 8 as it approaches its first beta, Commerce Guys gathered a variety of Drupal Commerce contributors and maintainers in its Paris office to begin active development on Drupal Commerce 2.x. The week long sprint began with architectural debate and validation incorporating the collective experience of our professional services teams and delivery partners.</p>
